gate: OPEN
task: S75-TB1
title: Fix Hardcoded Strings — language-selector + settings-screen
description: |
  Several user-visible strings are hardcoded in English instead of using i18n keys.
  Audit and fix all occurrences.

  Known hardcoded strings:

  1. language-selector.tsx line 38:
       <span className="...">Language</span>
     Fix: use t('settings.language')

  2. language-selector.tsx lines 47, 79:
       title="Select Language"
     Fix: use t('settings.selectLanguage') — add key to all 3 locale files.

  3. settings-screen.tsx line 187:
       <SelectorRow label="Help & Support" ...
     Fix: use t('settings.help')

  4. settings-screen.tsx line 188:
       <SelectorRow label="About NaviTrack" value="v1.0.0" ...
     Fix: label → t('settings.about')

  5. settings-screen.tsx line 192:
       <span>Rate app</span>
     Fix: use t('settings.rateApp')

  6. settings-screen.tsx line 200:
       <span>Log out</span>
     Fix: use t('settings.logout')

  New i18n keys to add across en.json / ru.json / uk.json:
    settings.selectLanguage:
      en: "Select Language"
      ru: "Выберите язык"
      uk: "Оберіть мову"
    settings.rateApp: already exists in en.json ✓ — add to ru.json and uk.json
    settings.logout: en: "Log out", ru: "Выйти", uk: "Вийти"
    settings.help: already en.json ✓ — add ru/uk
    settings.about: already en.json ✓ — add ru/uk

  Also audit ru.json and uk.json for any missing keys that exist in en.json.
  Add any missing keys with appropriate translations.

acceptance:
  - Zero hardcoded user-visible strings in language-selector.tsx
  - Zero hardcoded user-visible strings in settings-screen.tsx
  - Switching to Русский/Українська shows all settings labels translated
  - ru.json and uk.json contain all keys present in en.json

requires: [FRONTEND_DEV]
estimated: 1.5 hours
dep: S75-TA1
